snippet.title: Best VGM 2083 - Castlevania : Dracula X - Cemetery (Stage 4)
snippet.description:
See also:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Castlevania: Dracula X
Cemetery (Stage 4)
Tomoya Tomita, Masanari Iwata, Harumi Ueko & Masahiko Kimura
